title: 688. Early Look at Top College Prospects & Most Improved Teams
itunes:title: 688. Early Look at Top College Prospects & Most Improved Teams
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the duo look ahead and give an early look at the top college football prospects (:57). Then, the guys analyze which teams are the most improved teams heading into this season (20:18). Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
